1. *Čega* se on plaši? (What is he afraid of?)
2. Ona zna *čega* se sve tiče. (She knows what it's all about.)
3. On je uvek spreman da pomogne *čemu* je potrebno. (He is always ready to help what is needed.)
4. Ja ne znam *čega* se on toliko boji. (I don't know what he is so afraid of.)
5. Ne znam *čega* se on toliko raduje. (I don't know what he is so happy about.)
6. Ne znam *čega* se on boji. (I don't know what he is afraid of.)